data.description: This Huge Updated 4 Bedroom Parkwood Property featuring Front Foyer Entrance to Spacious Living Room with WW Carpeting and Bay Window with Opening Casements, Formal Dining Room with WW Carpet and Beautiful Full Kitchen with Clear Wood Cabinetry, Ceramic Tile Flooring, Electric Cooking and Ceiling Fan is One of the Best Values in the Northeast! The Second Floor Features Four Generous Sized Bedrooms with WW Carpeting and Full 3 PC Hall Bath with Tub Surround and Skylight. The Basement has Been Extended Into a Full 570' Family Room Perfect for Entertaining Friends and Family with WW Carpeting, Storage Closets, Natural Gas Fire Place, Separate Laundry/Mechanical Room, and, Front Entrance from Driveway and Rear Entrance to Concrete Patio and Fully Fenced Yard perfect for Bar-B-Ques. Trane Gas Hot Air Heat with Central Air Conditioning. Rear Exterior is Low Maintenance Stucco and Vinyl. This Home is Move In Ready!!
